Dry season 4-5 months with almost no rain; brooks intermittent. Annual fires £- cattie grazing in ali areas. Some spots with dense secondarv cha¬pada scrub ("carrasco"); much tabuleiro cleared to forra grassy pasture; much mata, caatinga & varjão in shifting cultivation.
